{"tid":494033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺工廈番工／出入嘅巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2017-12-09T07:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T09:16:09.000Z","uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"844ee2ec564a4aef64395c086b34cb52e2b5e0b3","tid":494033,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟係一個滿懷理想同熱誠嘅有為青年，矢志為香港工廈發展出一分微力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家幫緊大學做緊個有關工廈嘅research<br />\n各位出入工廈嘅巴打／絲打，可以的話幫幫手填份問卷，支持下。<br />\n你地嘅支持好緊要，因為如果份論文做得好嘅話，有機會可以俾政府個邊睇，希望可以幫助完善香港嘅工廈政策。<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FLPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b7e6cba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1</a><br />\n<br />\n拿哈比人我講多出做得到，J圖喺下面　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154143_377bf56d01e6b223160103fff94382bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154143_377bf56d01e6b223160103fff94382bb.jpg&h=9cc1c3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154144_38cc6467dea98ad3bb73534a963ad7de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154144_38cc6467dea98ad3bb73534a963ad7de.jpg&h=b96d9079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154146_3c8f9c3b5c3824c828f70ea86ad13453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154146_3c8f9c3b5c3824c828f70ea86ad13453.jpg&h=f617cc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uplo